text:
Photo: Jason Miller, Getty Images Cornerback TJ Carrie, breaking up a pass for Travis Benjamin in Cleveland, says the Raiders have “a mind-set of success.” Cornerback TJ Carrie, breaking up a pass for Travis Benjamin in...
CHICAGO — From when he brought in a “mind-set coach” in training camp, Raiders head coach Jack Del Rio has been hammering home positive thinking and positive energy to his players.
